text.tspan: Monthly confirmed cases of influenza A H1N1 (2009)
This shows the number of cases that were confirmed to have a strain of influenza A virus related to the H1N1
("Swine flu") pandemic that emerged in 2009. Only a fraction of potential cases of influenza are tested by labs
to confirm whether they have influenza and to identify their strain. The level of testing may vary between
